Package: preText2
Title: Diagnostics to Assess the Effects of Text Preprocessing Decisions
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matthew J.", "Denny", email = "mdenny@psu.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Arthur", "Spirling", email = "as9934@nyu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Functions to assess the effects of different text preprocessing
    decisions on the inferences drawn from the resulting document-term matrices
    they generate. This is an updated fork of the original preText package
    (Denny and Spirling, 2018, <doi:10.1017/pan.2017.44>) that is compatible
    with quanteda v4+.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    quanteda (>= 4.0),
    Matrix,
    ggplot2,
    parallel
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
